  <heading proof="needed">Operation of bingo and raffles.</heading>
  <text>Bingo and raffles may be conducted in the District only in accordance with <cite path="36">this title</cite>, any rules issued pursuant to <cite path="36">this title</cite>, and any other applicable law or rules.</text>
